          0,
          "Ligma was a clear signal this story is balls"
        ]
      ]
    ],
    [
      1,
      "p",
      [
        [
          0,
          [],
          0,
          "It’s part of an "
        ],
        [
          0,
          [
            4
          ],
          1,
          "old internet joke"
        ],
        [
          0,
          [],
          0,
          ", where, if you get it, you reply “Balls”. Try it. Say “Ligma Balls” out loud (preferably not in an open-plan office). You’ll see the (rather juvenile) joke."
        ]
      ]
    ],
    [
