      "p",
      [
        [
          0,
          [
            1
          ],
          1,
          "It’s a fake."
        ],
        [
          0,
          [],
          0,
          " Those reporters outside Twitter have been trolled by two guys with a sense of humour and some boxes. And they ran the story without independent corroboration. That’s ending up on my verification slides…"
        ]
      ]
    ],
    [
      1,
      "p",
      [
        [
          0,
          [],
          0,
          "Journalists with a little more awareness of internet culture quickly "
        ],
        [
          0,
