          ":"
        ]
      ]
    ],
    [
      1,
      "blockquote",
      [
        [
          0,
          [],
          0,
          "There are plenty of problems with what these two men say to reporters. The most glaring is that one man identifies himself as a software engineer named “Rahul Ligma.” "
        ],
        [
          0,
          [
            1
          ],
          1,
          "The Verge "
